enhanced_by.reason: Both methods involve generating an IPv6 address, which is a prerequisite for ipV6Cidr.
ipV6Cidr relies on the output of ipV6Address to form the CIDR notation.
Both methods generate CIDR notations, providing a basis for similar assertions.
The generated IPv6 address from getIpV6Address can be validated within the CIDR notation generated by ipV6Cidr.
